OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FCold on
OL,6,FFriday and Saturday with scattered
OL,7,Fshowers, wintry on hills. Rain
OL,8,Fspreading east followed by showers on
OL,9,FSunday.
